            </div>
            <div class="Item">
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">七</span><a href="/en/laws/link/597" target="_blank">長期信用銀行法</a>第十六条の八第一項の規定による指定</div>
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">(vii)</span>designation under Article 16-8, paragraph (1) of the Long-Term Credit Bank Act;</div>
            </div>
            <div class="Item">
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">八</span><a href="/en/laws/link/668" target="_blank">労働金庫法</a>第八十九条の十三第一項の規定による指定</div>
