            </div>
            <div class="Item">
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">九</span><a href="/en/laws/link/3601" target="_blank">銀行法</a>第五十二条の六十二第一項の規定による指定</div>
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">(ix)</span>designation under Article 52-62, paragraph (1) of the <a href="/en/laws/link/3601" target="_blank">Banking Act</a>;</div>
