            <div class="Item">
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">十一</span><a href="/en/laws/link/4090" target="_blank">保険業法</a>第三百八条の二第一項の規定による指定</div>
              <div class="ItemSentence"><span class="ItemTitle">(xi)</span>designation under Article 308-2, paragraph (1) of the <a href="/en/laws/link/4090" target="_blank">Insurance Business Act</a>;</div>
