        <div class="Article anchor" id="je_ch7at4">
          <div class="ArticleCaption">（指定紛争解決機関について準用する<a href="/en/laws/link/3601" target="_blank">銀行法</a>の規定の読替え）</div>
          <div class="ArticleCaption">(Replacement of Terms in Provisions of the <a href="/en/laws/link/3601" target="_blank">Banking Act</a> as Applied Mutatis Mutandis to Designated Dispute Resolution Organizations)</div>
