                    <div class="Sentence">funds transfer services (meaning the funds transfer services prescribed in Article 2, paragraph (2) of the <a href="/en/laws/link/3965" target="_blank">Payment Services Act</a> (Act No. 59 of 2009); the same applies in the following paragraph) or crypto-asset exchange services (meaning the crypto-asset exchange services prescribed in paragraph (7) of the relevant Article; the same applies in the following paragraph)</div>
