                    <div class="Sentence">funds transfer service provider, etc. (meaning the funds transfer service provider, etc. prescribed in Article 99, paragraph (1), item (viii) of the <a href="/en/laws/link/3965" target="_blank">Payment Services Act</a>; the same applies in Article 52-65, paragraph (2), Article 52-67, paragraph (3), and Article 52-79, item (i))</div>
